task.summary: Default task
Revised API for programs, attributes.
Some repairs and improvements due to recent IDC-Common merge
Revised API for cohorts, metadata
Utility to generate the 'filters' schema based on 'attributes' in the current DB.
Add manifest API and tests. Extended gen_filters_json.py to generate additional schemas.
Some changes to the data returned by the /attributes API

Fixed schema validation: add "additionProperties": True to filters schema. Had to post process json generation because it output "true" instead of "True". Fix some error checking to return more specific error codes. Add a simple test to check that schema validation is working.
Add another schema validation test.
Added cohort manifest preview api
Eliminated some options from /cohorts/{cohort_id}. Working on /collections API.
Multiple fixes, mostly for compatibility with new IDC version in the model.
Add 'None' option to cohort object hierarchy return.
Cleanup; test return_sql switch.
Added a /data_sources API, changed parameterization of /attributes. Better error checking in cohorts APIs.
Add /collections API
Several changes to the format of returned data. Bug fixes.
Metdata APIs pass authorization when calling the webapp.
Generate filterSet schema with minItems and maxItems requirements on all attributes. Add a bit of testing on these limits.
A few more subtests.
Removed "name" from collection metadata
Redesigned paging of cohort and metadata returns.
Move manifest tests into separate file and add paged versions of tests.
Removed legacy test_config.
Added copyright statement
Changed "idc_version" to "idc_data_version" everywhere to be clear what is versioned.
Not returning some extraneous metadata
Not returning some extraneous metadata
Not returning some extraneous metadata
Fixed names of manifest params
Change to workaround workspaces.xml conflict
Some fixes suggested by Suzanne needed to work in deployed environment.
